#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Select this option if you do <emphasis>not</emphasis> want to use a proxy "
#| "server."
msgid ""
"Select this option if you do <emphasis>not</emphasis> want to use a proxy "
"server and connect to the Internet directly."
msgstr ""
"Vælg dette hvis du <emphasis>ikke</emphasis> ønsker at bruge en proxy-server."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have decided to use a proxy, you have several methods to configure "
"the settings for it."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du besluttet dig for at bruge en proxy, har du adskillige metoder til "
"at indstille opsætningen for den."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:84
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Automatically detected script file"
msgid "Detect proxy configuration automatically"
msgstr "Automatisk detekteret script-fil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option if you want the proxy setup configuration script file to "
"be automatically detected and downloaded."
msgstr ""
"Vælg dette hvis du ønsker at proxyopsætningens indstillings-scriptfil skal "
"blive downloadet og detekteret automatisk."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This option only differs from the next choice in that it <emphasis>does "
#| "not</emphasis> require you to supply the location of the configuration "
#| "script file. Instead, it will be automatically downloaded using "
#| "<quote>Web Access Protocol Discovery</quote> (<acronym>WAPD</acronym>)."
msgid ""
"This option only differs from the next choice in that it <emphasis>does not</"
"emphasis> require you to supply the location of the configuration script "
"file. Instead, it will be automatically downloaded using <quote>Web Proxy "
"Auto-Discovery</quote> (<acronym>WPAD</acronym>) protocol."
msgstr ""
"Dette tilvalg er kun forskelligt fra det næste valg deri at det "
"<emphasis>ikke</emphasis> kræver at du angiver stedet for din indstillings-"
"scriptfil. I stedet for vil den automatisk blive taget ned ved brug af "
"<quote>Web Access Protocol Discovery</quote> (<acronym>WAPD</acronym>)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:98
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Automatically detected script file"
msgid "Use proxy auto configuration URL:"
msgstr "Automatisk detekteret script-fil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option if your proxy support is provided through a script file "
"located at a specific address. You can then enter the address in the "
"location text box, or use the <guiicon>folder</guiicon> icon to browse to it."
msgstr ""
"Vælg dette hvis din proxy-støtte er gennem en script-fil på en bestemt "
"adresse. Du kan så indtaste adressen i sted-tekstfeltet, elle bruge "
"<guiicon>mappe</guiicon>-ikonen til at finde den."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:108
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Automatically detected script file"
msgid "Use system proxy configuration:"
msgstr "Automatisk detekteret script-fil"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some systems are setup with $<envar>HTTP_PROXY</envar> to allow graphical as "
"well as non-graphical applications to share the same proxy configuration "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Nogle systemer er sat op med $<envar>HTTP_PROXY</envar> for at tillade "
"grafiske så vel som ikke-grafiske programmer at dele samme proxy-"
"indstillingsinformation."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
